    <note>Guo(1) Sanyi [8071] Zhixun's [945] father or uncle. Both Sanyi and his father, Zhuan [19842], are listed as Jiaxing, Jiaxing jinshi, but only Sanyi is also listed as a Changzhou jinshi. Since Zhuan's wife was a Changzhou, Wujin resident, I assume that Zhuan moved to Changzhou, which I identify as the address of both Sanyi and Zhuan's grandson, Zhixun [945]. Cheng Ju, WJ, 31.11a-13a. Zhejiang TZ, 124.8b; Jiahe zhi, 15.2b; Piling zhi, 11.12a. CBD, 3, 2129.</note>
